{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Investigate the failures in the administration of Civil Service Pensions",
        "additional_details": "The delays have caused significant financial hardship, emotional distress, and insecurity for individuals who have planned their retirements in good faith.\r\n\r\nParliament should scrutinise Capita\u2019s handling of pension administration, the government\u2019s oversight of the contract, and what immediate action is required to resolve outstanding cases, prevent further harm, and provide redress to those affected.",
        "background": "We call on Parliament to investigate the ongoing and systemic failures in the administration of civil service pensions. These failures have left thousands of current and former civil servants in limbo, waiting excessive periods for pension payments they are entitled to.",
